- Sample locations are specific sites where soil samples are collected for analysis.;

- 'sandy-skeletal' refers to a specific class of particle size in soil samples;
- 'top users' refers to users who have accessed the most pedons;
- 'top taxonomic names' refers to the taxonomic names ranked by depth within each taxonomic group.

